  "title": "How to find DiscordID",
  "messages": [
    {
      "content": "# Wondering how to find your DiscordID? Follow this guide!",
      "attachments": []
    },
    {
      "content": "> Open your User Settings > Go to Advanced > Enable Developer Mode",
      "attachments": [
        "/faqs-images/1371612722327715880/1-0.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "",
      "attachments": [
        "/faqs-images/1371612722327715880/2-0.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "> Once you have enabled Developer mode, right click on a user and click **”Copy ID”**",
      "attachments": []
    },
